---
title: Sweet & Spicy Pork Noodle Stir-Fry with Bell Pepper, Cilantro & Peanuts
description: This sweet and spicy noodle bowl will prove once and for all that home cooking beats takeout any day! Tender, chewy noodles are tossed with savory ground pork and crisp-tender bell pepper and scallions, then tossed with an umami-rich sweet soy and chili glaze. It’s all sprinkled with scallions, crunchy peanuts, and fresh cilantro, and finished with a squeeze of lime for bright contrast. Get ready to curl up in your favorite spot with a delicious bowl of lo mein straight from your kitchen!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/64ca4f07d1320bb7c7146ac2-c3d393f6.jpeg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipecards/card/64ca4f07d1320bb7c7146ac2.pdf
course: main course
servings: 2
source: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipes/sweet-spicy-pork-noodle-stir-fry-64ca4f07d1320bb7c7146ac2
time required: 30 minutes
nutrition:
  calories: 830 kcal
